snippet.title: Space Menace | Indie Game Trailers
snippet.description:
Space Menace is a real-time sci-fi space exploration and space battle game. You play as a space captain, seeking fortune and glory as you see fit. Leave your mark on the world and determine the fate of the galaxy with your decisions.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2000040/Space_Menace/
